divs: Sighting DetailsOnly took this picture because i take pictures of birds when ever i see them.Also my conure really seemed intrested in the area when i saw her looking in the tree's derection,she was making a low purr sound(sounds like a purr) Which means she intrested in somthing,and was very still.When i looked and saw the black birds she was intrested in i got my camera and took these shots,while secound snap she got scared and flew of to the other side of the room. I still continued to take the pictures of the birds. I did not notice anything untill i looked at what i got on camera.here are the pictures.
